Program: Outlook
Title: Outlook
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00g58b8
Last Broadcast Date: Thu 28 Apr 2011
Extraordinary personal stories from around the world. Today, a man whose wife died the day after she gave birth explains how he brought up his baby with the help of a blog. And the world's largest wedding guests - the elephants invited to Hindu ceremonies in India, and the man who handles them.